title: Looking For A Serious Silver Rank 5's Team!
body:
Looking for a silver rank 5's team to join. My main roles are Mid/Jungle Very Strong, I can also Top/Adc well... 
if you wanna add me thats ok :D
Ign: UnseenBlade

replies.body:
There are many Serious Silver ranked 5's teams around, you will do fine.

Most don't play online though due to travel time to and from LCS and play-off competitions.
